name: Oliver Nichols
summary: Oliver Nichols is a 31-year-old straight male based in Los Angeles, California. He originates from Seattle, Washington, and completed graduate studies at the University of Washington. In his career, Oliver is employed as a software developer in the tech industry, showing his intellectual capabilities. He speaks both English and Spanish, and his personal values are honesty, charity, and humor. He loves hiking, cooking, and programming and holds liberal political views. Religious belief-wise, he identifies as an agnostic. Regarding relationships, Oliver intends to enter a long-term monogamous relationship. His dating intentions appear to include plans for future parenthood as he does not currently have children but is open to having them. Oliver is a pet owner, specifically to a dog, and his fitness is well looked after as he someone who exercises regularly. The preferences for his partner include an age range of 25-35 years, non-smoker and is open to occasional drinking.
